OL,3,CHow can you avoid falling victim to a
OL,4,Cphone or online scam?
OL,6,FPensioners are most likely to confront
OL,7,Fscammers, as ITV News' Consumer Editor
OL,8,FChris Choi reports
OL,10,FScammers have long targeted older
OL,11,Fpeople seeing them as easy victims but
OL,12,Fthis tactic may soon come to an end.
OL,14,FOlder people are the most likely group
OL,15,Fin Britain to talk back to scammers,
OL,16,Fnew research by BT and Ability Net has
OL,17,Frevealed.
