OL,3,CHow can you avoid falling victim to a
OL,4,Cphone or online scam?
OL,6,FShe said: "(I just said) they're a
OL,7,Fscam and the lady at the other end
OL,8,Fsaid, well, how do you know I'm a scam?
OL,10,F"And I said, well, I'm not going to
OL,11,Ftell you, because I felt that I didn't
OL,12,Fwant them to learn from me in order to
OL,13,Favoid it in the future."
OL,15,FDespite the increased confidence of
OL,16,Folder people to confront scammers, the
OL,17,Fstudy shows almost a third of people
OL,18,Faged over 65 (27%) are not confident
OL,19,Fin their digital skills.
