OL,3,CHow can you avoid falling victim to a
OL,4,Cphone or online scam?
OL,6,FAmy Caton, a senior project manager at
OL,7,FBT Group, advised pensioners to
OL,8,Fcontinue to build their digital skills
OL,9,Fand ability to stay safe online.
OL,11,FShe told ITV News: "(Older people)
OL,12,Fdon't be scared by these experiences,
OL,13,Fuse it to fuel your learning."
