OL,3,CHow can you avoid falling victim to a
OL,4,Cphone or online scam?
OL,6,FWhether online or on your phone, avoid
OL,7,Fclicking on links or sharing personal
OL,8,For bank details. Scams involving HMRC
OL,9,Fare becoming more common, with
OL,10,Ffraudsters asking for personal tax
OL,11,Finformation.
OL,13,FDo your research
OL,15,FIf someone claiming to be from
OL,16,FMicrosoft calls you about a virus on
OL,17,Fyour computer, or if you receive a job
OL,18,Foffer that seems too good to be true,
OL,19,Fhang up and do your research.
