OL,3,CHow can you avoid falling victim to a
OL,4,Cphone or online scam?
OL,6,FContact the company directly to verify
OL,7,Fwhether it's a scam.
OL,9,FAsk family or friends
OL,11,FIf you are suspicious about a call or
OL,12,Ftext, ask a family member or friend to
OL,13,Fhelp verify whether the company is
OL,14,Flegitimate or a scam.
OL,16,FChange your passwords
OL,18,FReset all of your passwords, using a
OL,19,Fdifferent device to the one that may
OL,20,Fhave been compromised.
